#: scenario.xhp
msgctxt ""
"scenario.xhp\n"
"par_id3150364\n"
"help.text"
msgid "Choose <emph>Tools - Scenarios</emph>. The <emph>Create Scenario</emph> dialog appears."
msgstr "選擇<emph>[工具] - [分析藍本]</emph>。螢幕上會顯示<emph>[建立分析藍本]</emph>對話方塊。"

